<h2>ZOOM</h2>

<pre>   zoom: 8</pre>

<p>The second required part of the javascript text is 'zoom.' You can change this number depending on how much you want to map to be zoomed in on the location upon inital load of the page. The number of zoom can be selected from 0 to 18. The image below shows 0, 7, and 18.</p>

